ğŸ“Œ Project Overview

This project analyzes customer reviews from an e-commerce dataset using AWS AI and ML services.
It performs automated:

Sentiment Analysis

Key Phrase Extraction

Text Summarization

Data Storage & Processing

Interactive Dashboard Visualization

The final output is a QuickSight Dashboard showing insights such as sentiment distribution, ratings trend, product category analysis, and customer review summary.

