ğŸ”§ AWS Services Used
Service	Purpose
Amazon S3	Stores raw CSV data
AWS Lambda	ETL, Comprehend calls, Summarization trigger
Amazon Comprehend	Sentiment & key phrase extraction
Amazon DynamoDB	Structured storage of final processed data
Amazon SageMaker	Summary generation using prebuilt NLP model
Amazon QuickSight	Dashboard & visual insights
ğŸ§ª How It Works
1ï¸âƒ£ Upload Review File

Upload CSV â†’ ak-customer-datareview S3 bucket
This triggers the Lambda ingestion function.

2ï¸âƒ£ Processing Pipeline

Lambda:

Reads each row of the CSV

Cleans empty records

Calls Comprehend

Generates sentiment & key phrases

Writes processed data to DynamoDB (batch-write)

3ï¸âƒ£ Summarization

A second Lambda:

Reads all reviews from DynamoDB

Sends combined text to SageMaker endpoint

Stores final summary back in DynamoDB

4ï¸âƒ£ Visualization

QuickSight loads data from:

DynamoDB result export (CSV) OR

S3 exported file

User can interact with:

Filters

Charts

KPIs

Word clouds

Tables

